'''''A Dry White Season''''' ni filime yikinamico yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1989 iyobowe na Euzhan Palcy ikinwamo na Donald Sutherland, Jürgen Prochnow, Marlon Brando, Janet Suzman, Zakes Mokae naSusan Sarandon Yanditswe na Colin Welland na Palcy<ref>https://www.criterion.com/films/29148-a-dry-white-season</ref>, ishingiye ku gitabo cya André Brink cyitwa '''''A Dry White Season'''''<ref>https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/a-dry-white-season-1989</ref>. Robert Bolt nawe yatanze umusanzu wo gusubiramo amashusho atemewe<ref>https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/adrywhiteseasonrcooper_a09eab.htm</ref>. Yashyizwe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika yepfo]] mumwaka wa 1976 kandi ivuga kubyerekeye ivanguramoko . Brando yatorewe muri Oscar nk'umukinnyi witwaye neza<ref>https://mubi.com/films/a-dry-white-season</ref>.

== Umugambi ==
Mu 1976, muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] mu gihe cya apartheid, Ben Du Toit ( Donald Sutherland ) ni umwarimu w’ishuri ryo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo ku ishuri ry’abazungu gusa. Umunsi umwe<ref>https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-ca-mn-euzhan-palcy-dry-white-season-20190201-story.html</ref>, umuhungu w’umurimyi we, Gordon Ngubene ( Winston Ntshona ), yakubiswe n’abapolisi bera nyuma yo gufatwa n’abapolisi mu myigaragambyo y’amahoro hagamijwe politiki nziza y’uburezi ku birabura muri [[Afurika]] yepfo<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film951044.html</ref>. Gordon asaba Ben ubufasha. Ben amaze kwanga gutabara kubera ko yizeraga abapolisi, Gordon na we yafashwe na polisi kandi akorerwa iyicarubozo na Kapiteni Stolz ( Jürgen Prochnow ). Bitandukanye n'ubushake bw'umugore we Susan ( Janet Suzman ) n'umukobwa we Suzette ( Susannah Harker )<ref>http://www.thestudiotour.com/movies.php?movie_id=948</ref>, Ben agerageza kumenya byinshi ku ibura ry'umurimyi we wenyine. Nyuma y’ivumburwa ry’ubwicanyi bwakozwe na Gordon n’umuhungu we bombi<ref>https://www.britannica.com/topic/A-Dry-White-Season-film</ref>, Ben yahisemo kugeza iki kibazo imbere y’urukiko na Ian McKenzie ( Marlon Brando ) nk'umunyamategeko ariko aratsindwa. Nyuma yaho<ref>https://www.alamy.com/stock-photo/a-dry-white-season-1989-marlon-brando.html</ref>, akomeje gukora wenyine kandi ashyigikira itsinda rito ryabirabura, barimo umushoferi we Stanley Makhaya ( Zakes Mokae ), kugira ngo afashe abandi bateze imbere imibereho<ref>https://www.tcm.com/video/1128507/dry-white-season-a-1989-land-of-love-and-glory</ref>.

